Package: terrascoper
Title: Download Earth Observation Data from Terrascope STAC API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Weingartner", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download Earth observation products (Sentinel-5P, Sentinel-2,
    Sentinel-1, PROBA-V, etc.) from the Terrascope STAC API. Supports
    arbitrary bounding boxes, date ranges, and collections. Handles NetCDF,
    GeoTIFF, and other file formats. Authentication via environment variables.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports:
    rstac,
    httr,
    data.table
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
